quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,40,"Except, among them, Your chosen servants."
  15,41,"[Allāh] said, "
  15,42,"Indeed, My servants - no authority will you have over them, except those who follow you of the deviators."
  16,19,"And Allāh knows what you conceal and what you declare."
  16,20,"And those they invoke other than Allāh create nothing, and they [themselves] are created."
  16,21,"They are [in fact] dead,{1} not alive, and they do not perceive when they will be resurrected.",1:[i.e., inanimate or without understanding.]
